item.title: COGC009613 LG314/1211/20/038 - Construction and Augmentation of Recycled Water Assets for the Upgrade of the Elanora Recycled Water Pumping Station
item.description: The Principal wishes to appoint suitably experienced, qualified and equipped Contractor to undertake the construction and augmentation of recycled water assets for the upgrade of the Elanora Recycled Water Pumping Station and other associated works as required by the Principal.
